description: The First Trust India NIFTY 50 Equal Weight ETF (the "Fund"), formerly First Trust Taiwan AlphaDEX Fund, seeks investment results that correspond generally to the price and yield (before the Fund's fees and expenses) of an equity index called the NIFTY 50 Equal Weight Index (the "Index"). The Fund will normally invest at least 90% of its net assets (including investment borrowings) in common stocks that comprise the Index.
name: First Trust India NIFTY 50 Equal Weight ETF
